n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-indent:2em;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:2;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;&quot;&gt;“感谢建华建材集团给了我这样一次机会，感谢建华人在这几天的徒步中给我的帮助和鼓励！”这是几天以来我们听到最多的声音，也是建华建材集团的这些优秀合作伙伴们心底最诚挚的话语！&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-indent:2em;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-indent:2em;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-indent:2em;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:2;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;&quot;&gt;而何总的一句话，也说出了所有建华人的心声：“你们感谢建华给了你们这次机会，而我要说，是建华要感谢你们，没有你们就没有今天的建华！”是啊，无论是以前的合作之路，还是这几天的戈壁之路，抑或是今后建华建材集团的转型发展之路，这都是一个相互成就的过程，唯有携手同行，才能实现合作共赢！&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-indent:2em;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-indent:2em;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-indent:2em;&quot;&gt;\r\n		闭营晚宴的尾声，姚总与建华建材集团的营销精英们激情唱响《兄弟干杯》，为这场88公里的徒步盛事画上了一个圆满的句号。未来，有这群敢打敢拼、共创共担的精英们冲锋在前，有这群情深义重、鼎力相助的合作伙伴们携手同行，建华建材集团的转型发展之路一定会走得更快，更稳，更坚定！\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;ve